  m_text: "How to Play\nWelcome to the corporate battlefield. This is a turn-based
    tactical grid combat game. On your turn, use the mouse to move, cast abilities,
    or pass your turn. Highlighted tiles show where you can move or target. Abilities
    can damage enemies, heal allies, or apply status effects like Power Up, Power
    Down, and Shield. Win by using your team\u2019s skills and positioning to outmaneuver
    the opposition."
